<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3751885>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Tintiyakus sexangulus sp. nov. holotype male. A: habitus, lateral view; B: habitus, dorsal view; C: head, frontal view; D–F: Terminalia in dorsal, ventral and lateral view respectively. Abbreviations: Cer: cerci; Sty: styli; Pl: subgenital plate." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3751885/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3751894>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Tintiyakus trewicki sp. nov., holotype male. A: habitus, lateral view; B: habitus, dorsal view; C: head, frontal view; D–F: Terminalia in dorsal, ventral and lateral view respectively. Abbreviations: Cer: cerci; Sty: styli; Pl: subgenital plate." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3751894/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3751887>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Tintiyakus sexangulus sp. nov., male internal genitalia. A–B: phallus, ventral view; C–D: phallus, dorsal view. Abbreviations: TI: titillator process; EV: ejaculatory vesicles; DL: dorsal lobe(s); lw. vl.: lower folds of ventral lobe; up. vl.: upper folds of ventral lobe." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3751887/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3751890>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Tintiyakus sexangulus sp. nov., paratype female.A: habitus, lateral view; B: habitus, dorsal view; C–E: Terminalia in dorsal, ventral and lateral view respectively." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3751890/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3751896>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Tintiyakus trewicki sp. nov., male internal genitalia. A–B: phallus, ventral view; C–D: phallus, dorsal view. Abbreviations: TI: titillator process; EV: ejaculatory vesicles; DL: dorsal lobe(s); lw. vl.: lower folds of ventral lobe; up. vl.: upper folds of ventral lobe." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3751896/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3751900>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Geographical records of species Tintiyakus gen. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3751900/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3751898>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Tintiyakus piaroa comb. nov. (adapted from Derka et al. 2016). A. Terminalia in dorsal view; B. Terminalia in ventral view. Abbreviations: Cer: cerci; Sty: styli; Pl: subgenital plate." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3751898/files/figure.png" ;
